B.5 Machine Learning Accelerators

Neural Network Approximations:

¬∑ Learn effective action: S_eff[U] = NN(U)
¬∑ Generate configurations: Normalizing flows
¬∑ Critical slowing down: RL for cluster updates

Algorithm B.5.1 (Normalizing Flow for Gauge Fields):

```
# Forward: z ‚àº N(0,1) ‚Üí U = f_Œ∏(z)
# Train to match p(U) ‚àù e^{-S[U]}

Loss(Œ∏) = KL(q_Œ∏(U) || p(U))
        = ùîº_{z‚àºN(0,1)}[S(f_Œ∏(z))] - H(q_Œ∏)

# Sampling:
z ‚àº N(0,1)
U = f_Œ∏(z)  # independent sample!
```

Performance: O(1000)√ó speedup for decorrelated samples reported in simple models.

