These appendices provide the complete technical background, implementation details, verification protocols, and historical context for solving the Yang-Mills existence and mass gap problem. They represent the culmination of 7 generations of blueprint evolution, synthesizing mathematics, physics, computation, and community organization into a coherent plan for one of the greatest challenges in theoretical physics.